ille, California|Marysville]], [[California]]\n;[[Mexico]]\n*[[Torre\u00f3n]] and [[G\u00f3mez Palacio, Durango]] \n\n;Mexico\u2014United States border\n* [[San Diego|San Diego, California, United States]] and [[Tijuana|Tijuana, Baja California, Mexico]] \n* [[Calexico, California|Calexico, California, United States]] and [[Mexicali|Mexicali, Baja California, Mexico]]\n* [[Yuma, Arizona|Yuma, Arizona, United States]] and [[San Luis R\u00edo Colorado|San Luis R\u00edo Colorado, Sonora, Mexico]]\n* [[Nogales, Arizona|Nogales, Arizona, United States]] and [[Nogales, Sonora|Nogales, Sonora, Mexico]]\n* [[Douglas, Arizona|Douglas, Arizona, United States]] and [[Agua Prieta|Agua Prieta, Sonora, Mexico]]\n* [[Columbus, New Mexico|Columbus, New Mexico, United States]] and [[Las Palomas, New Mexico|Las Palomas, Chihuahua, Mexico]]\n* [[El Paso, Texas|El Paso, Texas, United States]] and [[Ciudad Ju\u00e1rez|Ciudad Ju\u00e1rez, Chihuahua, Mexico]]\n* [[Presidio, Texas|Presidio, Texas, United States]] and [[Ojinaga, Chihuahua|Ojinaga, Chihuahua, Mexico]]\n* [[Del Rio, Texas|Del Rio, Texas, United States]] and [[Ciudad Acu\u00f1a|Ciudad Acu\u00f1a, Coahuila, Mexico]]\n* [[Eagle Pass, Texas|Eagle Pass, Texas, United States]] and [[Piedras Negras, Coahuila|Piedras Negras, Coahuila, Mexico]]\n* [[Laredo, Texas|Laredo, Texas, United States]] and [[Nuevo Laredo|Nuevo Laredo, Nuevo Le\u00f3n, Mexico]]\n* [[McAllen, Texas|McAllen, Texas, United States]] and [[Reynosa|Reynosa, Tamaulipas, Mexico]]\n* [[Brownsville, Texas|Brownsville, Texas, United States]] and [[Matamoros, Tamaulipas|Matamoros, Tamaulipas, Mexico]]\n;[[Canada\u2013United States border]]\n*[[Point Roberts, Washington]] and [[Tsawwassen|Tsawwassen, British Columbia]]\n*[[Pembina, North Dakota]] and [[Emerson, Manitoba]]\n*[[International Falls, Minnesota]] and [[Fort Frances|Fort Frances, Ontario]]\n*[[Sault Ste. Marie, Michigan]] and [[Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario]]\n*[[Port Huron, Michigan]] and [[Sarnia|Sarnia, Ontario]]\